## Context Window: The Memory Limit

**Definition:** Every model has a context window—its maximum "working memory" measured in tokens.

### Context Window Sizes by Model

| Model | Context Window | Capacity |
|-------|-----------------|----------|
| GPT-3.5 (older) | 8k tokens | ~6,000 words |
| Claude 3.5 Sonnet | 200k tokens | ~150,000 words or 500 pages |
| Gemini 1.5 Pro | 1M+ tokens | Massive capacity |

### What Happens at the Limit

- Exceed the context window → model **silently truncates earlier context**
- **It literally forgets the start of your conversation**
- This is why long conversations may lose context from earlier messages

